au14-trait-drugallergy-name = Random Drug Allergy
au14-trait-drugallergy-desc = You are allergic to one of a handful of common medications. Ingesting it triggers a serious allergic reaction until treated with naloxone or epinephrine. You spawn with an epinephrine injector and a tag noting your allergy.
au14-drug-allergy-tag-name = medical alert tag
au14-drug-allergy-tag-text = Allergic to { $reagent }
au14-drugallergy-reaction = Your throat tightens and your skin crawls - something is very wrong!
au14-drugallergy-building = Your skin crawls as the reaction spreads through you.
au14-drugallergy-suffering = You can't breathe - your body is shutting down!
au14-drugallergy-stun = Your muscles suddenly seize up!
au14-drugallergy-cured = The reaction subsides almost instantly as the medication takes hold.

au14-alert-allergicreaction-name = Allergic Reaction
au14-alert-allergicreaction-desc = You're suffering a severe allergic reaction. Treat with naloxone or epinephrine immediately.
